And so let's look at it.

97
00:05:47,070 --> 00:06:01,580

98
00:06:01,580 --> 00:06:05,170
So what you can see is, you have
these in your hand out,

99
00:06:05,170 --> 00:06:08,890
we have four graphs,
four plots.

100
00:06:08,890 --> 00:06:10,920
And I won't show you
them all because

101
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:13,080
they're all are identical.

102
00:06:13,080 --> 00:06:17,080
What they all give me is a mean
