132
00:08:17,390 --> 00:08:20,990
pictures can be deceiving.

133
00:08:20,990 --> 00:08:27,710

134
00:08:27,710 --> 00:08:31,740
There can be no doubt about the
utility of graphics for

135
00:08:31,740 --> 00:08:34,740
